  "texts": [
    "The features are used to build a Random Forest classifier.",
    "The transformation was primarily developed for MTSC, but can be applied to univariate series.",
    "Figure 10 shows the relative rank performance, and Table 3 summarises the overall performance statistics.",
    "All four pipelines are significantly more accurate than 1-NN DTW.",
    "Excluding feature extraction and using Rotation Forest rather than Random Forest with TSFresh increases accuracy by over 0.05."
  ]
